cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY, cs.CR 

This paper deals with wireless networks and interference modeling, which are topics related to computer networks (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of directional antennas and power control also involves signal processing (cs.MM) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the Attacking Case metric, which is related to security and cryptography (cs.CR).
